</paragraph>
<paragraph pageId="63" pageNumber="64">
<taxonomicName class="Insecta" family="Vespidae" genus="Sphex" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="Sphex semifossulatus" order="Hymenoptera" pageId="63" pageNumber="64" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="semifossulatus">Sphex semifossulatus</taxonomicName>
van der Vecht, 1973: 349. Substitute name for 
<taxonomicName class="Insecta" family="Vespidae" genus="Sphex" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="Sphex argentifrons" order="Hymenoptera" pageId="63" pageNumber="64" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="argentifrons">Sphex argentifrons</taxonomicName>
