. A ♂, habitus B ♂, frontal view of clypeus C collecting localities, those of 
<taxonomicName class="Insecta" family="Vespidae" genus="Sphex" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="Sphex cognatus" order="Hymenoptera" pageId="63" pageNumber="64" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="cognatus">Sphex cognatus</taxonomicName>
and 
<taxonomicName class="Insecta" family="Vespidae" genus="Sphex" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="Sphex latilobus" order="Hymenoptera" pageId="63" pageNumber="64" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="latilobus">Sphex latilobus</taxonomicName>
